                     <interp inst="t18291029-232-person1903" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have a shawl, pawned on Saturday week, by the prisoner.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I took it up, as I thought there had been some woman in the place; the prosecutor said if I would give it up, he would not appear against me.</p>
